ovarian cancer on August 12th, 2000

00:12:30.110 --> 00:12:34.370
at the age of 87, while staying

00:12:34.370 --> 00:12:37.579
at the home of her sister Georgina Montavon

00:12:37.579 --> 00:12:42.589
the wife of Ricardo Montavon.  Judy

00:12:42.589 --> 00:12:44.959
Lewis the daughter of Loretta Young and

00:12:44.959 --> 00:12:47.660
Clark Gable will die of cancer on

00:12:47.660 --> 00:12:53.000
November 25th,  2011 at the age of 76,

