51 years after her father Clark Gable's

00:12:57.259 --> 00:13:00.800
death and 11 years after her mother

00:13:00.800 --> 00:13:04.939
Loretta Young. The same year 1935 that

00:13:04.939 --> 00:13:07.500
Clark Gable stared with Loretta Young

