his famous mustache to get the part. He

00:13:24.090 --> 00:13:27.240
felt better after being nominated for

00:13:27.240 --> 00:13:30.570
the academy award. The next year he will

00:13:30.570 --> 00:13:33.330
star with Jeanette MacDonald in San

00:13:33.330 --> 00:13:37.920
Francisco and in 1937 he'll be paired

00:13:37.920 --> 00:13:41.940
with a younger actress Jean Harlow in

00:13:41.940 --> 00:13:45.150
Saratoga. Harlow had been in poor health

00:13:45.150 --> 00:13:47.820
before filming began and on the

00:13:47.820 --> 00:13:50.700
29th of May,  during a love scene

00:13:50.700 --> 00:13:53.640
Harlow actually collapsed in Gables arms

00:13:53.640 --> 00:13:54.960
from exhaustion.

