Doctors diagnosed her with gall bladder

00:13:58.440 --> 00:14:01.470
infection. After several days and not

00:14:01.470 --> 00:14:05.250
returning to the set, Gable visits Jean

00:14:05.250 --> 00:14:08.880
at her home. He becomes concerned when he

00:14:08.880 --> 00:14:12.270
sees her condition. On the 6th of June

