in 1939 before Gable gets his divorce from

00:15:11.800 --> 00:15:15.370
Maria Langham and is able to marry

00:15:15.370 --> 00:15:18.760
Carole Lombard. That same year Clark

00:15:18.760 --> 00:15:21.310
Gable with star in his most famous role

00:15:21.310 --> 00:15:26.200
as Rhett Butler in Gone with the Wind.

