divorcing Clark. She will date other

00:15:40.600 --> 00:15:44.589
actors but she will never remarry.  She will

00:15:44.589 --> 00:15:47.860
eventually return to Houston. She will

00:15:47.860 --> 00:15:52.390
pass away on September the 24th 1966 at

00:15:52.390 --> 00:15:54.279
the age of 82.

00:15:54.279 --> 00:15:56.620
She's buried in the Glendale cemetery in

00:15:56.620 --> 00:15:57.910
Houston.

00:15:57.910 --> 00:16:00.760
She'll be remembered in Houston society

00:16:00.760 --> 00:16:04.390
as once being the wife of Clark Gable.

